
Slackware Current Repository by Conraid

======================================================================

termbox2 (suckless terminal rendering library)

termbox2 is a terminal rendering library that retains the suckless
spirit of the original termbox (simple API, no dependencies beyond
libc) and adds some improvements (strict error checking, more
efficient escape sequence parsing, code gen for built-in escape
sequences, opt-in support for 32-bit color, extended grapheme
clusters, test suite).

HOME: https://github.com/termbox/termbox2

